4.2.1

## v4.2.1 Release Notes (2025-07-09)

### New Features - ai-trackdown-tools Integration
- **ai-trackdown-tools Integration** - Comprehensive integration with persistent ticket management
- **Documentation Updates** - Added ai-trackdown-tools configuration across all user guides
- **Troubleshooting Guide** - Comprehensive troubleshooting section for ai-trackdown-tools
- **Agent Configuration** - ai-trackdown-tools integration in custom agent configuration
- **Framework Overview** - Enhanced architecture documentation with ai-trackdown-tools

### Technical Enhancements
- **Persistent Ticket Management** - Cross-process ticket persistence for multi-agent coordination
- **Configuration Integration** - ai-trackdown-tools configuration in framework.yaml
- **Fallback Mechanisms** - Graceful degradation when ai-trackdown-tools is unavailable
- **Agent Permissions** - Granular permissions for ticket operations per agent
- **Directory Organization** - Updated directory structure documentation

### Documentation Updates
- **docs/FRAMEWORK_OVERVIEW.md** - Added ai-trackdown-tools architecture section
- **docs/user-guide/01-getting-started.md** - Added dependency setup instructions
- **docs/user-guide/04-directory-organization.md** - Added configuration information
- **docs/user-guide/05-custom-agents.md** - Added ai-trackdown-tools configuration
- **docs/user-guide/07-troubleshooting-faq.md** - Added troubleshooting section
- **docs/INDEX.md** - Updated with new references and command examples

## v4.2.0 Release Notes (2025-07-09)

### New Features - User Configuration Directory
- **~/.claude-multiagent-pm/** - New user configuration directory structure
- **User-Defined Agents** - Custom agent system in ~/.claude-multiagent-pm/agents/user-defined/
- **Configuration Management** - YAML-based configuration in ~/.claude-multiagent-pm/config/
- **Template System** - Enhanced templates in ~/.claude-multiagent-pm/templates/
- **Training Modifications** - Agent training enhancements in ~/.claude-multiagent-pm/agents/training-modifications/

### Technical Enhancements
- **Directory Structure** - Migrated from ~/.claude-pm/ to ~/.claude-multiagent-pm/
- **Agent Architecture** - Enhanced user-defined agent loading system
- **Configuration Format** - YAML-based configuration for improved flexibility
- **Template Engine** - Advanced template system for rapid development
- **Documentation Updates** - Comprehensive documentation updates for v4.2.0

### Directory Features
- **User Directory** - ~/.claude-multiagent-pm/ for all user configurations
- **Agent Management** - Centralized agent definitions and custom agents
- **Configuration Hierarchy** - Structured configuration management
- **Template Library** - Comprehensive template system for projects and agents
